a farcaster v2 frame based on Christopher Alexander's "A Pattern Language"

Functionality 
- select a random pattern from the book every day
- summarize the pattern
- generate an image to describe the solution
- send a notification to the user to check today's pattern

Resources:
- Frames v2 specifications: https://docs.farcaster.xyz/developers/frames/v2/spec
- A Pattern Language Patterns: https://github.com/zenodotus280/apl-md/tree/70c6d6e7d3c54284724b1cacdf0590bf530c9eaa/Patterns
